---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<section id="experience">
  <!-- Hero Stats Section -->
  <div class="experience-hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <p class="hero-subtitle">MI TRAYECTORIA HABLA POR MÍ</p>
      <h1 class="hero-title">
        THE VOICE OF<br />
        <span class="highlight-text">FRONTEND DEVELOPMENT</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="hero-description">
        Con mi profunda experiencia y conocimiento del sector, ofrezco
        desarrollo experto y soluciones a medida que impulsan el éxito de cada
        proyecto, actuando como el puente confiable entre la visión del cliente
        y la realidad del mercado.
      </p>

      <div class="stats-container">
        <div class="stat-item">
          <div class="stat-number">500%</div>
          <div class="stat-label">DE CRECIMIENTO DESDE 2019</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <div class="stat-number">+50</div>
          <div class="stat-label">PROYECTOS COMPLETADOS CON ÉXITO</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <div class="stat-number">3</div>
          <div class="stat-label">AÑOS DE EXPERIENCIA PROFESIONAL</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Professional Journey Section -->
  <div class="journey-section">
    <div class="journey-header">
      <p class="journey-subtitle">SOBRE MI CEO Y FUNDADOR</p>
      <h2 class="journey-title">RAFA CARMONA</h2>
      <p class="journey-description">
        Rafa Carmona es un visionario y pionero en el sector del desarrollo
        frontend, reconocido como uno de los desarrolladores más influyentes
        según la comunidad tech. Nacido en Extremadura y con una carrera inicial
        en ingeniería, Rafa llevó su talento para identificar tendencias
        emergentes al desarrollo web moderno.
      </p>
      <p class="journey-description">
        Su liderazgo innovador ha establecido nuevos estándares de calidad y
        servicio. Rafa promueve una filosofía empresarial basada en la
        transparencia, la ética y la sostenibilidad, inspirando a otros con su
        integridad y compromiso. Su capacidad para prever y adaptarse a las
        necesidades del mercado ha sido ampliamente reconocida, posicionando su
        trabajo como referente de excelencia y confianza en el desarrollo web
        global.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Experience Timeline Section -->
  <div class="timeline-section">
    <div class="timeline-header">
      <h2 class="timeline-title">TRAYECTORIA PROFESIONAL</h2>
      <p class="timeline-subtitle">
        Un recorrido de excelencia y crecimiento continuo
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="timeline-container">
      <!-- Current Position -->
      <div class="timeline-item current">
        <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <div class="timeline-period">Sep 2023 - Present</div>
          <h3 class="position-title">
            Freelance Developer
            <Icon class="external-link" name="arrow-up-right" size="1.2rem" />
          </h3>
          <div class="company-info">
            <p class="company-description">
              <strong>Main languages:</strong> React, Angular, TypeScript, JavaScript,
              HTML, CSS, SASS.<br />
              <strong>Participated in</strong> 7+ projects for top-tier companies.<br
              />
              <strong>Extensive experience</strong> with web and mobile browsers
              ensuring responsiveness.<br />
              <strong>Android and iOS</strong> development experience.<br />
              <strong>Unit and user testing</strong> with Jest and Playwright.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="tech-stack">
            <span class="tech-pill">React</span>
            <span class="tech-pill">Angular</span>
            <span class="tech-pill">Next</span>
            <span class="tech-pill">React Native</span>
            <span class="tech-pill">TypeScript</span>
            <span class="tech-pill">HTML5</span>
            <span class="tech-pill">CSS3</span>
            <span class="tech-pill">Astro</span>
            <span class="tech-pill">Canva</span>
            <span class="tech-pill">PhotoShop</span>
            <span class="tech-pill">Adobe Illustrator</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Mobbeel Experience -->
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <div class="timeline-period">Aug 2023 — Aug 2024</div>
          <h3 class="position-title">
            Mobbeel Solutions SL
            <Icon class="external-link" name="arrow-up-right" size="1.2rem" />
          </h3>
          <div class="company-info">
            <p class="company-description">
              <strong>Main languages:</strong> React, Angular, TypeScript, JavaScript,
              HTML, CSS, SASS.<br />
              <strong>Participated in</strong> 7+ projects for top-tier companies.<br
              />
              <strong>Extensive experience</strong> with web and mobile browsers
              ensuring responsiveness.<br />
              <strong>Android and iOS</strong> development experience.<br />
              <strong>Unit and user testing</strong> with Jest and Playwright.
            </p>
            <p class="achievement">
              • Designed and developed a web portal in Angular, reducing manual
              errors and saving <strong>up to 70% of the time</strong><br />
              • Developed a new back-office system with successful presentation<br
              />
              • Fully designed and developed a QR screen feature for a major banking
              firm<br />
              • Created mockups focused on <strong>UX/UI</strong> and followed <strong
                >WCAG accessibility guidelines</strong
              >
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="tech-stack">
            <span class="tech-pill">React</span>
            <span class="tech-pill">Angular</span>
            <span class="tech-pill">TypeScript</span>
            <span class="tech-pill">JavaScript</span>
            <span class="tech-pill">HTML5</span>
            <span class="tech-pill">CSS3</span>
            <span class="tech-pill">Jest</span>
            <span class="tech-pill">Playwright</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Wa.Works Experience -->
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <div class="timeline-period">Nov 2021 — Mar 2023</div>
          <h3 class="position-title">
            Wa.Works - Wide Assessment (Bergen, Norway)
            <Icon class="external-link" name="arrow-up-right" size="1.2rem" />
          </h3>
          <div class="company-info">
            <p class="company-description">
              <strong>Experience with</strong> React Hooks, Redux, Context API, and
              TypeScript.<br />
              <strong>Committed to</strong> finishing projects before departure and
              maintaining high standards.<br />
              <strong>International experience</strong> working remotely with Norwegian
              teams.
              <p class="achievement">
                • Successfully finished the last project before departure<br />
                • Presented project to the CEO<br />
                • Mentored a teammate and participated in pair programming sessions<br
                />
                • International remote work experience with Norwegian teams
              </p>
            </p>

            <div class="tech-stack">
              <span class="tech-pill">React</span>
              <span class="tech-pill">Redux</span>
              <span class="tech-pill">TypeScript</span>
              <span class="tech-pill">Context API</span>
              <span class="tech-pill">HTML5</span>
              <span class="tech-pill">CSS3</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Call to Action Section -->
  <div class="cta-section">
    <div class="cta-content">
      <h2 class="cta-title">¡CONVIÉRTETE EN CLIENTE!</h2>
      <p class="cta-description">
        ¿Listo para llevar tu proyecto al siguiente nivel? Trabajemos juntos
        para crear soluciones web excepcionales.
      </p>
      <a href="#contact" class="cta-button"> CONOCE MIS PROYECTOS </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <style>
    #experience {
      background: var(--background-dark);
    }

    /* Hero Section Styles */
    .experience-hero {
      padding-top: 4rem;
      background:
        linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(30, 56, 96, 0.95), rgba(45, 74, 90, 0.85)),
        url("/images/modern-office-setup.jpg") center/cover;
      min-height: 80vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
      color: white;
      position: relative;
    }

    .hero-content {
      max-width: 900px;
      padding: 2rem;
    }

    .hero-subtitle {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      color: var(--primary-color);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .hero-title {
      font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.1;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      color: white;
    }

    .highlight-text {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color), #7dd3fc);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      display: inline-block;
    }

    .hero-description {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto 3rem auto;
    }

    .stats-container {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 3rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .stat-item {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .stat-number {
      font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #2ecc71;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .stat-label {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    /* Journey Section */
    .journey-section {
      background: var(--background-test2);
      padding: 5rem 2rem;
      color: white;
    }

    .journey-header {
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .journey-subtitle {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      color: var(--primary-color);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .journey-title {
      font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #d4af37;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }

    .journey-description {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      text-align: justify;
    }

    /* Timeline Section */
    .timeline-section {
      padding: 5rem 2rem;
      background: var(--background-dark);
    }

    .timeline-header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 4rem;
    }

    .timeline-title {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 3vw, 2.8rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      color: white;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .timeline-subtitle {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
      font-weight: 400;
    }

    .timeline-container {
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      position: relative;
    }

    .timeline-container::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      left: 2rem;
      top: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      width: 2px;
      background: linear-gradient(
        to bottom,
        var(--primary-color),
        rgba(94, 232, 232, 0.3)
      );
    }

    .timeline-item {
      position: relative;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      padding-left: 5rem;
    }

    .timeline-item.current .timeline-marker {
      background: #2ecc71;
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(46, 204, 113, 0.5);
    }

    .timeline-marker {
      position: absolute;
      left: 1.2rem;
      top: 1rem;
      width: 1.6rem;
      height: 1.6rem;
      background: var(--primary-color);
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 3px solid var(--background-dark);
      z-index: 2;
    }

    .timeline-content {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
      padding: 2rem;
      border-radius: 1rem;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      transition:
        transform 0.3s ease,
        box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    }

    .timeline-content:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    }

    .timeline-period {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--primary-color);
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .position-title {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: white;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .external-link {
      color: var(--primary-color);
      opacity: 0.7;
      transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
    }

    .position-title:hover .external-link {
      opacity: 1;
    }

    .company-info {
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .company-description {
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .achievement {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
      padding: 1rem;
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
      border-left: 3px solid var(--primary-color);
    }

    .tech-stack {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }

    .tech-pill {
      background: rgba(94, 232, 232, 0.2);
      color: var(--primary-color);
      padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem;
      border-radius: 1rem;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      border: 1px solid rgba(94, 232, 232, 0.3);
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .tech-pill:hover {
      background: rgba(94, 232, 232, 0.3);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    /* Call to Action Section */
    .cta-section {
      background: linear-gradient(
        135deg,
        rgba(30, 56, 96, 0.95),
        rgba(16, 32, 58, 0.9)
      );
      padding: 4rem 2rem;
      text-align: center;
      color: white;
    }

    .cta-content {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .cta-title {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      color: white;
    }

    .cta-description {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      background: var(--primary-color);
      color: var(--background-dark);
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 1rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .cta-button:hover {
      background: #7dd3fc;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(94, 232, 232, 0.3);
    }

    /* Responsive Design */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .experience-hero {
        min-height: 60vh;
        padding: 1rem;
      }

      .hero-content {
        padding: 1rem;
      }

      .stats-container {
        gap: 2rem;
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      .journey-section,
      .timeline-section {
        padding: 3rem 1rem;
      }

      .timeline-container::before {
        left: 1rem;
      }

      .timeline-item {
        padding-left: 3rem;
      }

      .timeline-marker {
        left: 0.2rem;
      }

      .tech-stack {
        justify-content: center;
      }
    }
  </style>
</section>
